# Next.js 16 auto-generates these on every build; not source.
AGENTS.md
CLAUDE.md

# Per-UniProt DeepTMHMM topology JSONs are *generated artifacts* —
# `scripts/build_structure_viewer_data.py` writes them here from the
# external DeepTMHMM cohort under
# `data/external/deeptmhmm_surfaceome_predictions/`. They should
# eventually land in D1 under the deep-dive schema (PR #23) and be
# fetched at request time. For now we ship a single mock
# (`O95800.json` for GPR75) so the v1.0.0 viewer demo is self-contained;
# the rest are gitignored. Regenerate locally with:
#
#   uv run python scripts/build_structure_viewer_data.py
#
public/structure-viewer/*
!public/structure-viewer/O95800.json
# SRC (P12931, GLOB by DeepTMHMM — myristoyl-anchored cytoplasmic
# kinase). Generated with `--include-globular` because most truly
# soluble proteins should skip the membrane-topology viewer, but
# lipid-anchored cytoplasmic proteins belong on the surfaceome and the
# AFDB structure is still informative for the reader.
!public/structure-viewer/P12931.json
